    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div style="font-family: 'STKaiti', 'SimSun', 'Source Han Serif SC', serif; line-height: 1.8; color: #2c3e50; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1rem;"><!-- 标题区域 --><div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #4a6572 50%, #2c3e50 100%); color: white; padding: 3.5rem 2rem 3rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0 4rem 0; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); min-height: 280px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; border-radius: 18px; width: 100%;"><div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background:     radial-gradient(circle at 20% 40%, rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.4) 0%, transparent 50%),    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 60%, rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),    repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 2px, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 4px);"></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 2;"><div style="font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 'STKaiti', serif; line-height: 1.2; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">八声甘州·孤馆秋</div><div style="width: 120px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.6), transparent); margin: 1.5rem auto; opacity: 0.7;"></div><div style="font-size: 1.3rem; opacity: 0.95; margin: 0; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0 1rem;">记同途风雨岁华深，<br>殷勤共此襟</div><div style="margin-top: 2rem;"><div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);">宋词 · 秋日之思</div></div><div style="margin-top: 2.5rem;"><div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);"><span style="font-weight: 300; display: flex; align-items: center;"><svg style="width: 16px; height: 16px; margin-right: 0.4rem;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5c-1.11 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L3 20c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V10h14v10zM5 6v2h14V6H5z"/></svg>2026-03-10</span><span style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); font-size: 0.8rem;">|</span><span style="font-weight: 300; display: flex; align-items: center;"><svg style="width: 16px; height: 16px; margin-right: 0.4rem;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 17.25V21h3.75L17.81 9.94l-3.75-3.75L3 17.25zM20.71 7.04c.39-.39.39-1.02 0-1.41l-2.34-2.34c-.39-.39-1.02-.39-1.41 0l-1.83 1.83 3.75 3.75 1.83-1.83z"/></svg>原创词作</span><span style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); font-size: 0.8rem;">|</span><span style="font-weight: 300; display: flex; align-items: center;"><svg style="width: 16px; height: 16px; margin-right: 0.4rem;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 3v10.55c-.59-.34-1.27-.55-2-.55-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4s1.79 4 4 4 4-1.79 4-4V7h4V3h-6z"/></svg>八声甘州</span></div></div></div></div><div style="position: relative; z-index: 1; margin-top: 0;"><div style="background: rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.08); padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin: 0 0 3rem 0; border-left: 4px solid #9b59b6; min-height: 180px;"><div style="color: #6c3483; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">📜 词牌简介 · 八声甘州</div><div style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem; padding: 0.5rem 0;">《八声甘州》简称《甘州》，唐边塞曲，因全词共八韵，故称"八声"。双调九十七字，前后段各九句、四平韵。此调音节慷慨悲壮，宜于抒发苍凉激越之情。柳永"对潇潇暮雨洒江天"为此调千古绝唱。本词依正格填制，于孤馆秋深中抒离愁别绪，寄重逢期盼。</div></div><div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.1), rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.05)); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.2); margin: 2.5rem 0; font-style: italic; color: #4a5568; position: relative; min-height: 200px;"><div style="position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 25px; background: white; color: #9b59b6; padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">词前小序</div><div style="padding-top: 1.2rem; font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.9;">丙辰年秋夜，独宿孤馆。窗外梧叶萧萧，灯前孤影寂寂。忆昔年风雨同途，殷勤共济；叹今朝音书杳杳，孤馆秋深。纵有新鞍逸趣，难遣旧梦寒侵。念繁华逐浪，谁记当初苦共斟？长漏永夜思无那，唯愿卿珍重赴遥岑。待他年重过柴桑径，停骖听鸟，共话旧时心。遂填此词，以慰孤馆秋思。</div></div><h2 id="词文详析"><a href="#词文详析" class="headerlink" title="词文详析"></a>词文详析</h2><div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f5eef8 0%, #ebdef0 100%); border: 2px solid #9b59b6; border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.8rem; margin: 2.8rem 0; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); min-height: 380px;"><div style="position: absolute; top: -16px; left: 25px; background: #9b59b6; color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">上阕</div><div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><div style="color: #6c3483; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-family: 'STKaiti', serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">记同途风雨岁华深，殷勤共此襟。</div><div style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 2; font-size: 1.15rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">嗔言路险，怨叹途贫，无复珠琛。<br>未许芳尘驰远陌，霜迹印青襟。<br>一别音书杳，孤馆秋深。</div></div><div style="background: rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.1); padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 2.2rem; border-left: 3px solid #9b59b6; min-height: 250px;"><div style="color: #6c3483; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.15rem;">🌧️ 上阕解析 · 风雨同途</div><div style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>"记同途风雨岁华深，殷勤共此襟。"</strong> 开篇追忆，温情脉脉。"同途风雨"既是实写旅途艰辛，亦喻人生坎坷。"岁华深"言时光悠长，"殷勤共此襟"写携手同心之态。一个"记"字统领全词，开启回忆之门。<br><br><p><strong>“嗔言路险，怨叹途贫，无复珠琛。”</strong> 细节生动，写尽旅途艰辛。”嗔言””怨叹”是当时真实情态，略带娇嗔的抱怨更显亲密。”无复珠琛”既写路途贫瘠无珍宝，亦暗喻人生际遇的贫乏。三句白描，如在目前。<br><br></p><p><strong>“一别音书杳，孤馆秋深。”</strong> 陡转现实，对照鲜明。从热闹的回忆跌入孤寂的现实。”音书杳”三字写尽离别后的牵挂与失望，”孤馆秋深”以景结情，秋之萧瑟、馆之孤寂、夜之深沉，三重意象叠加，愁绪满纸。</p></div></div></div><div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8f4fc 0%, #f3e8fd 100%); border: 2px solid #8e44ad; border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.8rem; margin: 2.8rem 0; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); min-height: 400px;"><div style="position: absolute; top: -16px; left: 25px; background: #8e44ad; color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">下阕</div><div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><div style="color: #5b2c6f; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-family: 'STKaiti', serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">纵有新鞍逸趣，奈旧梦难遣，夜夜寒侵。</div><div style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 2; font-size: 1.15rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">念繁华逐浪，谁记苦同斟？<br>更长漏永思无那，卿当珍重赴遥岑。<br>他年约，过柴桑径，停骖听鸟音。</div></div><div style="background: rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.1); padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 2.2rem; border-left: 3px solid #8e44ad; min-height: 280px;"><div style="color: #5b2c6f; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.15rem;">🌙 下阕解析 · 夜梦重逢</div><div style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>"纵有新鞍逸趣，奈旧梦难遣，夜夜寒侵。"</strong> 矛盾心理，深刻真实。"新鞍逸趣"写现在生活的新鲜趣味，但"纵有""奈"转折有力，新欢不敌旧梦。"夜夜寒侵"写梦境之频繁、思念之刻骨，一个"寒"字既写秋夜之寒，亦写心境之寒。<br><br><p><strong>“念繁华逐浪，谁记苦同斟？”</strong> 世态炎凉之叹，亦含自问自省。”繁华逐浪”喻世人追逐名利如逐浪花，转瞬即逝。”谁记苦同斟”既是问世人，亦暗含对自身坚守的确认——我仍记得当年共饮苦酒的情谊。<br><br></p><p><strong>“他年约，过柴桑径，停骖听鸟音。”</strong> 结尾温暖明亮，寄予美好期盼。”柴桑径”用陶渊明典故，喻归隐田园之路。”停骖听鸟音”画面恬静，意境悠远——停下马车，静听鸟鸣，共享自然之趣。这不仅是地理上的重逢，更是心灵上的归真。</p></div></div></div><h2 id="三重情感脉络"><a href="#三重情感脉络" class="headerlink" title="三重情感脉络"></a>三重情感脉络</h2><div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f3e8ff 0%, #e9d8fd 100%); border: 2px solid #9f7aea; border-radius: 18px; padding: 3rem; margin: 3rem 0; box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(159, 122, 234, 0.12); min-height: 450px;"><div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.8rem;"><div style="color: #553c9a; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">🌊 情感发展三重境</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-style: italic;">从风雨同途到孤馆秋深，从夜夜寒侵到停骖听鸟</div></div><div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2.2rem; margin: 2.5rem 0;"><div style="background: white; padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-top: 4px solid #9b59b6; position: relative; overflow: hidden; min-height: 280px;"><div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; width: 70px; height: 70px; background: rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.1); border-radius: 0 0 0 70px;"></div><div style="color: #6c3483; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">👥 第一境 · 风雨同途</div><ul style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 1.05rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>记同途风雨岁华深</strong> - 深情追忆往昔</li><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>嗔言路险怨叹途贫</strong> - 艰辛中的亲密</li><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>殷勤共此襟</strong> - 携手同心的温暖</li><li><strong>霜迹印青襟</strong> - 岁月留下的痕迹</li></ul><div style="color: #9b59b6; font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic; padding-top: 1.2rem; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;">"殷勤共此襟"——衣袖相连，心意相通</div></div><div style="background: white; padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-top: 4px solid #8e44ad; position: relative; overflow: hidden; min-height: 280px;"><div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; width: 70px; height: 70px; background: rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.1); border-radius: 0 0 0 70px;"></div><div style="color: #5b2c6f; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">🏮 第二境 · 孤馆秋深</div><ul style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 1.05rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>一别音书杳</strong> - 离别后的寂寥</li><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>孤馆秋深</strong> - 环境映衬心境</li><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>夜夜寒侵</strong> - 思念的无孔不入</li><li><strong>更长漏永思无那</strong> - 长夜漫漫的煎熬</li></ul><div style="color: #8e44ad; font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic; padding-top: 1.2rem; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;">"夜夜寒侵"——梦境如寒夜，思念如冷风</div></div><div style="background: white; padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-top: 4px solid #3498db; position: relative; overflow: hidden; min-height: 280px;"><div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; width: 70px; height: 70px; background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1); border-radius: 0 0 0 70px;"></div><div style="color: #1a5276; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">🌿 第三境 · 重逢之盼</div><ul style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 1.05rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>卿当珍重赴遥岑</strong> - 深情的嘱托</li><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>他年约过柴桑径</strong> - 田园重逢的约定</li><li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong>停骖听鸟音</strong> - 恬静美好的想象</li><li><strong>从孤寂到期盼</strong> - 情感的升华</li></ul><div style="color: #3498db; font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic; padding-top: 1.2rem; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;">"停骖听鸟音"——停下奔忙，聆听自然与心声</div></div></div></div><h2 id="艺术特色分析"><a href="#艺术特色分析" class="headerlink" title="艺术特色分析"></a>艺术特色分析</h2><div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #fff8e1 0%, #fff3cd 100%); border: 2px solid #d4a017; border-radius: 18px; padding: 3rem; margin: 3rem 0; box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.1); min-height: 400px;"><div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;"><div style="color: #8b4513; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">🎭 艺术特色分析</div><div style="color: #a68a64; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-style: italic;">今昔对照、细节传神、用典自然、情感真挚</div></div><div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 2.2rem; margin: 2.5rem 0;"><div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); min-height: 320px;"><div style="color: #8b4513; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0e6d2; padding-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">🔄 今昔对照</div><div style="margin-top: 1.2rem;"><div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><div style="color: #c05621; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">同途风雨 vs 孤馆秋深</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;">上阕热闹温暖的回忆与下阕孤寂凄清的现状形成强烈对比。"风雨同途"的艰辛中有温情，"孤馆秋深"的静谧中藏孤寂。</div></div><div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><div style="color: #c05621; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">新鞍逸趣 vs 旧梦难遣</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;">现实的新鲜趣味与记忆的深刻烙印形成矛盾。外在的新鲜无法替代内心的旧梦，凸显情感的执着。</div></div><div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><div style="color: #c05621; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">繁华逐浪 vs 苦同斟</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;">世人的浮躁追逐与当年的真挚情谊形成对比。在"繁华逐浪"的喧嚣中，凸显"苦同斟"情谊的珍贵。</div></div></div></div><div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); min-height: 320px;"><div style="color: #8b4513; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0e6d2; padding-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">🎨 细节与用典</div><div style="margin-top: 1.2rem;"><div style="margin-bottom: 1.8rem;"><div style="color: #c05621; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">嗔言怨叹的细节</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;">"嗔言路险，怨叹途贫"八个字，通过娇嗔抱怨的细节，生动再现了当年旅途中的亲密互动，使回忆充满生活气息。</div></div><div style="margin-bottom: 1.8rem;"><div style="color: #c05621; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">柴桑径的典故</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;">"柴桑径"暗用陶渊明归隐典故。陶渊明柴桑人，辞官归隐。此处既指归隐之路，又喻心灵回归本真之地，用典自然贴切。</div></div><div style="margin-bottom: 1.8rem;"><div style="color: #c05621; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">停骖听鸟的意境</div><div style="color: #718096; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;">"停骖听鸟音"创造了一个宁静美好的画面：停下奔忙的马车，在田园小径上静听鸟鸣。这既是想象中的重逢场景，也是理想的生活状态。</div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="词中名句赏析"><a href="#词中名句赏析" class="headerlink" title="词中名句赏析"></a>词中名句赏析</h2><div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e8f6f3 0%, #d1f2eb 100%); border: 2px solid #1abc9c; border-radius: 18px; padding: 3rem; margin: 3rem 0; box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(26, 188, 156, 0.1); min-height: 350px;"><div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;"><div style="color: #148f77; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">✨ 词中名句赏析</div><div style="color: #5d6d7e; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-style: italic;">匠心独运处，最是动人心</div></div><div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;"><div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-left: 4px solid #9b59b6;"><div style="color: #6c3483; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.15rem;">🌙 "纵有新鞍逸趣，奈旧梦难遣，夜夜寒侵"</div><div style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">此三句写尽新旧情感的矛盾。"新鞍逸趣"比喻新鲜事物带来的乐趣，但"纵有"与"奈"的转折，凸显旧情难忘。"夜夜寒侵"既写秋夜之寒，更写梦境之冷——旧梦如寒夜，时时侵入，无法抵挡。十四字中，有对比，有转折，有隐喻，情深意切。</div></div><div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-left: 4px solid #8e44ad;"><div style="color: #5b2c6f; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.15rem;">🍂 "一别音书杳，孤馆秋深"</div><div style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">十字写尽离别后的孤寂。"音书杳"三字，包含了多少等待与失望；"孤馆秋深"四字，融情入景，将孤寂、秋意、夜深沉三重意象叠加。馆孤、人孤、心亦孤；秋深、夜深、情亦深。以景结情，余韵无穷。</div></div><div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-left: 4px solid #3498db;"><div style="color: #1a5276; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.15rem;">🌿 "他年约，过柴桑径，停骖听鸟音"</div><div style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">结尾三句如画，亦如诗。"柴桑径"用典而不晦涩，喻归隐自然；"停骖听鸟"动静结合——停下奔忙（停骖），静听天籁（听鸟）。这不仅是未来的约定，更是理想的生活境界：从尘世喧嚣回归自然宁静，从孤寂思念走向心灵重逢。</div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">以&#39;记同途风雨岁华深&#39;起笔，追忆风雨同途岁月，抒发孤馆秋深之思，终寄&#39;他年约，过柴桑径&#39;的重逢期盼</summary>
    
    
    
